title: [Castle Varunar, Keep]
description: The spiral staircase abruptly ends here.  This cramped room appears to be the very top of the castle keep.  A pair of rusted iron manacles has been bolted to the stone walls.  A small bed of blood stained rushes is the only other evidence that anyone has ever been here.
